quran[190]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"∆Åadanike yim…ìe …ìen hasboore ma…ì…ìe nden, te kam…ìe hi…ìe e nder welsindaare ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe"
  21,2,Arataa e ma…ì…ìe waaju immorde ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe ko fu…ó…óaa si wanaa …ìe jentike nde hara kam…ìe hi…ìe fija
  21,3,"∆Åer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko welsandii…óe …ìen too√±u…ìe suu…óa cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, hara oo wonu si wanaa …ìanndinke yeru mo'on, kaa on aray e mbilewu hara onon hi…óon sutii (ndaara)"
  21,4,"O maaki: \"Joomi am no Anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi Kanko ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo On"
  21,5,"Ko woni, …ìe wi'u: \"Ko nde jii…ìu-jaa…ìu koy…ói, toode, o fefindi nde, ko woni, kanko ko o yimoowo, awa yo o addan en Aayewal wano aran…ìe …ìen Nuliranoo non"
  21,6,"Gom…óinaali ado ma…ì…ìe immorde e saare Men halki nde. Enee, hara ko kam…ìe goom…óita"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa si wanaa wor…ìe Men Wahayina e ma…ì…ìe, lanndee yim…ìe defte …ìen si tawii wonii on anndaa. @Corrected"
  21,8,"Men wa…óaali …ìe …ìalli …ìe √±aamataa √±aametee, …ìe laataaki kadi luttintee…ìe"
  21,9,"Refti Men Goonginani …ìe Fodoore nden Men danndi …ìe wonndude e …ìen …ìe Men Muuyi, Men halki fantin…ìe …ìen"
  21,10,Gom…óii Men jippinii faade e moo…óon Deftere no e nder mayre ja≈ãtawol moo…óon. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,11,Heewii ko Men halki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko too√±unde Men fu…ó…ói …ìaawo mayre yim…ìe goo
  21,12,"Tuma nde …ìe so'unoo Lepte Amen …óen, tawi kam…ìe hi…ìe doga …óe"
  21,13,"Wata on dogu, ruttee faade e ko neemina…óon kon e mu'un e ko…óan…óe mo'on, belajo'o on lannditoyte"
  21,14,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, menen men laatinoke too√±u…ìe\". @Corrected"
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu ma…ì…ìe, haa Men wa…óa …ìe co√±ateeri ko …ìe may…ìe"
  21,16,Men tagaali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Men fijoo…ìe
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faandino nde Men jogotoo fijindaaru, Men jogitotono …óum immorde ka Amen si tawii Men laatike wa…óoo…ìe"
  21,18,"Ko woni, Me…óen werloo Goonga kan e dow meere nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko sifoto…óon"
  21,19,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi …ìen wonu…ìe ka Makko kadi …ìe mawnittaako gaayi rewugol Mo, …ìe hasrintaaka kadi"
  21,20,Hi…ìe Subhinoo jemma e √±alorma …ìe aamataa
  21,21,"Kaa …ìe jogiti rewetee…ói ka leydi hara kannji hi…ói immintina [may…ìe …ìen]"
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin] rewtee…ói ko wonaa Alla …ói bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin gaayi ko…ìe sifotoo. @Corrected"
  21,23,"O lanndetaake ko O gollata kon, kam…ìe ko …ìe lannditoytee…ìe"
  21,24,"Kaa …ìe jogiti gaanin Makko rewetee…ói? Maaki: \"Addee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni ja≈ãta …ìen wonndu…ìe e am e ja≈ãta …ìen adii…ìe lam\". Ko woni, …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe …ìe anndaa Goonga kan kam…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe"
  21,25,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo si wanaa Men wahayinii e makko; pellet, rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Min Rewee Lam"
  21,26,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Hinnorante On jogitike …ìi…ó…óo\". Senayee woodanii Mo, ko woni, […ìen ko …ìe] jeyaa…ìe teddinaa…ìe"
  21,27,"∆Åe adortaa Mo konngol ngol, kam…ìe ko Yamiroore Makko nden …ìe gollata"
  21,28,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso ma…ì…ìe e ko woni kon hedde …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, …ìe tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo O Weltanii, kam…ìe immorde e kulol Makko ko …ìe jootu…ìe"
  21,29,"Kala e ma…ì…ìe kadi wi'u…óo: \"Min ko mi rewetee…óo gaanin Makko\". On …óon Men Yo…ìay mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Men Yo…ìirta too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  21,30,"Enee, hara …ìen yeddu…ìe yi'aali wonndema kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin …ói laatinoke hippondir…ói, Men Udditi …ói Men wa…ói immorde e ndiyam …óam kala huunde wuuru nde. Kaa …ìe gom…óintaa"
  21,31,"Men wa…ói ka leydi pelle fii wata nde oo√±odo e ma…ì…ìe, Men wa…ói e mayri …óate yaaju…óe, belajo'o kam…ìe …ìe feeway"
  21,32,"Men wa…ói kammu ngun kippudi reenaandi, kam…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe gaayi Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  21,33,Ko Kanko woni On Tagu…óo jemma on e √±alorma on e naange ngen e lewru ndun kala majji hi…ói fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku
  21,34,"Men wa…óanaali …ìanndunke ado maa…óa luttineede, enee, hara si a maayii ko kam…ìe woni luttintee…ìe …ìen"
  21,35,"Kala wonkii meedat may…óe nden, Men jarribora on bone on e mo∆¥∆¥ere nden jarrabagol, ko ka Amen kadi ruttoto…óon"
  21,36,"Si …ìen yeddu…ìe yi'ii ma, …ìe jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde […ìe wi‚Äôa:] \"Enee, hara ko oo woni on ja≈ãtotoo…óo rewetee…ói mo'on …óin?\" hara kam…ìe ko …ìe yeddu…ìe jantagol Hinnorante On"
  21,37,"Ne…ó…óake on Tagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am …óen wata on hawju"
  21,38,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on goongu…ìe"
  21,39,"Sinndo …ìen yeddu…ìe anndiino tuma tawi …ìe ittataa Yiite ngen ka geece ma…ì…ìe wanaa kadi ka …ìabbe ma…ì…ìe kadi, kam…ìe …ìe wonaali walloytee…ìe"
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee nge muga …ìe, hara …ìe hattantaake ruttugol nge, …ìe wonaali kadi nennanoytee…ìe"
  21,41,"Gom…óii Nulaa…ìe goo jalkitanooma ado maa…óa, jippii e …ìen jalkitu…ìe ko …ìe laatinoo hi…ìe jalkita"
  21,42,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e √±alorma immorde e Hinnorante On, ko woni, kam…ìe gaayi ja≈ãta Joomi ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe"
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani …ìe reewetee…ìe …ìe no dannda …ìe gaanin Amen? ∆Åe hattantaake wallude hay wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, wanaa kam…ìe woni wondatee…ìe immorde e Amen"
  21,44,"Ko woni, Men dakmitii …ìee e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen haa ngurndam …óam juutani …ìe. Enee, hara …ìee yi'aali wonnde Menen Me…óen ara e leydi ndin Men ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kam…ìe woni fooloo…ìe …ìen"
  21,45,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko mi woni jertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndun, si …ìe jertinaama"
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii …ìe see…óa immorde e Lepte Joomi maa …óen, maa …ìe wi'a: \"Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, menen men laatinoke too√±u…ìe"
  21,47,"Men wa…óa manndikir…óe(peesir…óe) Nun…óal ngal fii √ëalnde Darngal hara wonkii woo to√±iroytaake hay e huunde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Men adday kun Men yonii Hasboo…ìe"
  21,48,Gom…óii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e ja≈ãta wonannde huloo…ìe …ìen
  21,49,∆Åen hulay…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe ka wirnii hara kam…ìe immorde e Darngal ngal ko …ìe huli
  21,50,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] ko nde Ja≈ãta, ko nde barkinaande Men Jippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yedday…ìe nde"
  21,51,"Gom…óii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Men laatike kadi Anndu…ìe mo"
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Ko hon…óum woni …óii nanndonlaaji nate mahii…óe, …óin …ói ufini…óon e [dewal] mu'un"
  21,53,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men taw baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen no rewde …ói"
  21,54,"O maaki: \"Gom…óii on laatike onon e baabiraa…ìe mon …ìen e nder majjere …ìanngunde won…óon"
  21,55,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, ko Goonga kan addan…óaa men, kaa an ko e fijoo…ìe …ìen jeya…óaa"
  21,56,"Maaku: \"Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin On Tagu…óo…ói, min komi jeyaa…óo e seedii…ìe …ìen e dow …óum"
  21,57,"Mi woondirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii …óii sanamuuji mo'on …ìaawo huccitugol mo'on ko on ru≈ãii …ìe"
  21,58,"O wa…ói …ói kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, belajo'o kam…ìe …ìe ruttoto e mayru"
  21,59,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko hommbo wa…ói …óu'un e rewetee…ói amen …óin? Pellet, on ko o jeyaa…óo e too√±u…ìe …ìen"
  21,60,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men naniino suka no ja≈ãtoo …ói ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa"
  21,61,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Addee mo yeeso gite yim…ìe …ìen, belajo'o …ìe seedoto"
  21,62,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, Ibraahiima ko an wa…ói …óu'um …óoo e rewetee…ói amen …óin"
  21,63,"O maaki: \"Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle …óum, lanndee…ói si tawii …ói laatike hi…ói wowla"
  21,64,"∆Åe ruttii faade e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'i: \"Pellet, ko onon woni too√±u…ìe …ìen"
  21,65,"Refti …ìe uggini ko'e ma…ì…ìe …óen […ìe wi'i:] gom…óii hi…óa anndi …ói'i wonaa wowlay…ói"
  21,66,"O maaki: \"Enee, on reway gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e huunde hara lorrataa on kadi"
  21,67,Bis mo'on e kon ko rewoton gaanin Alla. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,68,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Sunnee mo, wallee rewetee…ói mo'on …óin, si tawii ko on golloo…ìe"
  21,69,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo yiite, laato …ìuu…ìol e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima"
  21,70,∆Åe faandanii mo pewje Men wa…ói …ìe pertube …ìen
  21,71,"Men danndi mo [Men danndi kadi] Luutu faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barkini e mu'un wonannde tageefooji …óin"
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka …ìeydugol, kala ma…ì…ìe Men wa…ói […ìe] mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe"
  21,73,"Men wa…ói …ìe Almaamii…ìe hi…ìe fewna e Yamiroore Amen Men Wahayini faade e ma…ì…ìe gollugol mo∆¥∆¥i …óin e √±innugol Julde nden e Okkugol Jakka on, …ìe laatinoke ko …ìe Reway …ìe Men"
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo √ëee√±al e Ganndal, Men danndi mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yim…ìe mu'un] laatinoo no golla so…ìu…ói …óin, pellet, kam…ìe …ìe laatinoke yim…ìe bon…ìe faasiqii…ìe"
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  21,76,"E Nuuhu tuma nde o noddunoo ko adii, Men jaabinani mo kanko e …ìeynguure makko nden immorde e sa…óteende mawnde nden"
  21,77,"Men walli mo immorde e …ìen yim…ìe fennu…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Pellet, kam…ìe …ìe laatino yim…ìe bon…ìe, Men yooli …ìe, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe"
  21,78,E Daawuuda e Sulaymaana tuma nde …ìe √±aawaynoo fii ngesa mban tuma nde bonnunoo e nder mabba dammi yim…ìe …ìen Men woni seedii…ìe √±aawoore ma…ì…ìe nden
  21,79,"Men Faamini nde Sulaymaana [√±aawoore nden] gooto-kala e ma…ì…ìe Men Okki √ëee√±el e Ganndal Men elti wonndude e Daawuuda pelle …óen hi…óe subhinoo e colli …óin kadi, Men laatike gollu…ìe"
  21,80,"Men Anndini [Daawuuda] mo∆¥∆¥inngol meke√±aaji fii mo'on, fii yo …ói reenu on immorde e hare mo'on. Taw si onon ko on jarnoo…ìe"
  21,81,"[Men eltani] Sulaymaana henndu ndun ko ndu bippooru hindu doga e yamiroore makko, faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barki e mu'un. Men laatike Anndu…ìe kala huunde"
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji …óin, …óin …ói no mutana mo, …ói golla golle gaanin …óum. Men laatanike …ói Reenoo…ìe"
  21,83,"[Ja≈ãto kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] \"Min dey memii lam lorra kan, ko An woni ∆Åuroowo Yurmeede yurmtoo…ìe …ìen"
  21,84,"Men jaabinani mo Men hunci ko he…ìi mo kon immorde e lorra, Men Okkiti mo …ìeynguure makko nden e yeru ma…ì…ìe wonndude e ma…ì…ìe kadi, …óum ko Yurmeende immorde ka Amen e waaju wonannde rewoo…ìe …ìen"
  21,85,"[Ja≈ãto kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, …ìen fow ko e mun√±…ìe …ìen …ìe jeyaa"
  21,86,"Men naadi …ìe e nder Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kam…ìe ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  21,87,"[Ja≈ãto kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahunoo ko o tikku…óo o sikki wonnde Men Hattanaake e hoore makko, o noddi ka ni…ìe; \"Wonnde rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa An Senayee wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaa…óo e too√±u…ìe …ìen"
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndi mo immorde e suno ngon, ko wano nii kadi Men danndirta gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  21,89,"[Ja≈ãto kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wata A …óalam bajjo, ko An woni ∆Åur…óo Mo∆¥∆¥ude ronoo…ìe …ìen"
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo, Men Okki mo Yahyaa, Men mo∆¥∆¥inani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kam…ìe …ìe laatinoke hi…ìe yaccoo e [gollugol] mo∆¥∆¥i …óin hi…ìe nodda Men ka rer…óere e kulol …ìe laatinoke yannkinanii…ìe Men"
  21,91,"[Ja≈ãto kadi fii] oya [suddii…óo] reenunoo…óo farju makko on Men wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu Amen, Men wa…ói mo kanko e ge…óaljo makko on Maande wonannde winndere nden"
  21,92,"Pellet, …óee mofte mo'on ko mofte goote, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam"
  21,93,"∆Åe ta∆¥i fiyaake ma…ì…ìe on hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, …ìe fow ko faade ka Am …ìe ruttoytoo"
  21,94,"Kala gollu…óo immorde e mo∆¥∆¥u…ói …óin hara kanko ko o gom…óin…óo, dullugol alaa fii golle makko …óen, pellet, Menen Men winndanay mo"
  21,95,"No Harmani saare nde Men halki …óum, wonnde kam…ìe …ìe ruttataako [ton]"
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Yaajuuja e Maajuuja, hara kam…ìe immorde e kala na…óel hi…ìe sortoo"
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nden …ìadike, tawi kayre puttini gii…óe …ìen yeddu…ìe, […ìe wi'a:] \"Eeyoo bone amen, gom…óii men laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e …óu'um, ko woni, men laatike too√±u…ìe"
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyay…ìe e magge"
  21,99,Sinndo …ìee laatinoke rewetee…ìe …ìe jolataano e magge. ∆Åe fow ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe luttintee…ìe e nder magge
  21,100,"No woodani …ìe e nder magge haraango, kam…ìe …ìe nanataa nder ton"
  21,101,"Pellet, …ìen …ìe mo∆¥∆¥i …óin adanii …óum immorde ka Amen …ìen …óon ko …ìe wo…ó…óintintee…ìe gaayi magge"
  21,102,"∆Åe nanoytaa wuu…óaango magge kam…ìe hi…ìe e nder ko wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin lokaa(woo…óa) kon, ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe"
  21,103,"Suninoytaa…ìe …óen∆¥ere mawnde nden, Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen no ja…ì…ìoo…ìe […ìe wi'a:] \"Ko ndee woni √ëalaande mo'on, nden nde laatino…óon hi…óon fodee"
  21,104,"√ëalnde Men taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol …óerol defte. Ko wano Men fu…ó…óori non ka arannde tagu Men ruttirta ngu, […óum] ko Fodoore e dow Amen, pellet, Menen Men laatike golloo…ìe"
  21,105,"Gom…óii Men winndiino ka Jabuura …ìaawo Alluwal Reenaangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaa…ìe Am mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen ronoyta ndi"
  21,106,"Pellet,no e …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] jottingol wonannde yim…ìe rewoo…ìe …ìen"
  21,107,Men Nuliraali ma si wanaa Yurmeende wonannde winndire nden
  21,108,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonndema Rewetee…óo mon On ko O Rewetee…óo Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbilii…ìe?\". @Corrected"
  21,109,"Si tawii …ìe …óurnike, maaku: \"Mi anndinii on e dow fotondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no …ìadii maa…óum si no wo…ó…ói kon ko foda…óon"
  21,110,"Pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi ko fee√±i kon e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suu…óoton"
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, belejo'o …óum ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne"
  21,112,"Maaku: \"Jooma, √ëaawir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On woni Wallitortee…óo On e dow kon ko sifoto…óon"
  22,1,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, hulee Joomi mo'on, pellet, dillannde Darngal ngal ko huunde mawnde"
  22,2,"√ëalnde yi'oton ngal, yejjitoyay kala muyninoowo ko o muyninaynoo kon, fukka kala sowii…óo ko o sowiinoo kon, a yi'ay yim…ìe …ìen no siwri, hara kam…ìe …ìe siwraa, kono Lepte Alla …óen ko sa…ótu…óe"
  22,3,"No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal, o jakka kala Seytaane canndallo"
  22,4,"Winndaama e hoore-makko wonnde pellet, kala weldu…óo e makko pellet, o majjinay mo, o …óowa mo haa ka Lepte Sa'iiri"
  22,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, si tawii on laatike e sikke immorde e immital ngal, pellet, Menen Men Tagii on immorde e mbullaari refti e to…ì…ìere maniiyu, refti e he…ó…óere refti e huyre timmunde tagu e nde wonaa timmunde tagu fii yo Men …ìannginan on, Me…óen √ëii…ìina ka renngaaji ko Men Muuyi kon haa e happu innaa…óo, refti Men yaltini on ko on booboo…ìe, refti fii yo on yotto sagatalaaku mo'on no e mo'on …ìen …ìe no maaya no e mo'on kadi …ìen …ìe no ruttee faade ka …ìuri jaasude e ngurndan …óam fii wata …ìe anndu …ìaawo ganndal hay e huunde. A yi'ay leydi ndin ko yoorunde si Men jippinii e dow mayri ndiyam …óan ndi dilla ndi ∆¥ura ndi fu…óina immorde e kala noone woo…óu…óo"
  22,6,"∆äum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurnitay may…ìe …ìen, tawde pellet, ko O Hattan…óo e dow kala huunde. @Corrected"
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, wonnde pellet, Alla immintinay …ìen won…ìe ka genaale"
  22,8,No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wanaa peewal wanaa deftere nur…óunde(jalbunde)
  22,9,"Hofu…óo balaaji mu'un [mawnintinii…óo] fii yo o majjin gaayi Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna oyeere Men mee…óinoyay mo kadi √ëalnde Darngal Lepte sumoowe ngen"
  22,10,"∆äum ko sabu ko juu…óe maa…óa …óen ardini kon. E wonnde pellet, Alla wonaali Too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  22,11,"No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si mo∆¥∆¥ere he…ìii mo o tabitira sabu …óum si jarrabuyee kadi he…ìii mo o waylitoo e yeeso makko, o hayrii aduna on e Laakara on ko …óum tigi woni hayrere …ìanngunde nden"
